<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/7dbdfc8aed4cf8dba6df11212a4e78522.png"></span><span>Chicken at Heart III</span></dt><dd><div>Increases strength by 20% when HP is 60%<br>or above, but decreases strength by 20% when<br>HP is less than 60%. Also, every time the<br>Deadly Joyride skill hits enemies three times,<br>the user's defense will be reduced by 10% for<br>five seconds, but their attack skill damage will<br>be increased by 5%. This skill damage buff can<br>stack up to an increase of 100%, but all stacks<br>will be lost upon using an attack skill.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9f9540aa3b892c485f82bfd1ef78b1b72.png"></span><span>Potent Stun Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>stunned them, their strength is increased by 15%<br>for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will not<br>activate again for 15 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/25ef50e0a0cfce84d2ec98ed78c188702.png"></span><span>Primed Devastation +10%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases the critical rate of the adventurer you<br>are currently controlling by 10% for 5 seconds<br>every time their initial skill, displayed at the<br>top of their skill list, becomes available for use.<br>After activating, this ability will not<br>activate again for 15 seconds.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div>The adventurer Yuya&#39;s Deadly Joyride Lv. 4 skill, which can be unlocked with his mana spiral, hits more often, has a wider range, and can be more easily directed than the same skill at Lv. 3 and below. The easier it is to change direction, the more hits players can reliably land on enemies.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.</div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1607234400,update_time1607066843